Description: Installation of new kitchen cabinetry as per design.
Installation of quartz countertops in the kitchen.
Demolition of existing fixtures, walls, and finishes in the full apartment including the kitchen and bathroom.
Tear out existing bathroom fixtures and finishes.
Complete rewiring of apartment including installation of new outlets, switches, and a new electrical panel.
Install new engineered wood flooring throughout.
Painting of all walls and ceilings with Benjamin Moore Regal Select.
Replacement of plumbing fixtures including sink, toilet, and relevant piping.
Installation of new floor and wall tiles in the bathroom.
